	<div class="entry-content">
		<p>Samira Kawash is most recently the author of <i>Candy: A Century of Panic and Pleasure</i>.</p>
<p><b>Author:</b> <a href="http://candyprofessor.com/" onclick="_gaq.push(['_trackEvent', 'outbound-article', 'http://candyprofessor.com/', 'Samira Kawash']);"   target="_blank">Samira Kawash</a></p>
<div class="powerpress_player" id="powerpress_player_554"><object type="application/x-shockwave-flash" data="http://www.edrants.com/wp-content/plugins/powerpress/audio-player.swf" id="554" height="24" width="290">
